    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在霓虹灯点缀的赛博反乌托邦中，迎战无尽的敌人浪潮！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武装自己，选择你的武器，投身于一场生存之战，对抗无休止的敌人攻击。每次击杀都能为你赢得经验值，解锁商店中的强力技能和升级。提升等级，强化装备，掌握新能力，在无限的猛攻中不断前行！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319710/extras/23b54e045b4b58b9371e0522e9e83a70.poster.avif?t=1734581207\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319710/extras/23b54e045b4b58b9371e0522e9e83a70.webm?t=1734581207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319710/extras/23b54e045b4b58b9371e0522e9e83a70.mp4?t=1734581207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在激烈的战斗中，抓住机会获取临时强化道具，比如无限弹药、生命值提升、伤害增加和速度增强。这些奖励能助你在战斗中占据优势，击败敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一波攻击都会更加激烈，敌人更强，挑战更长。震慑、燃烧、反击，守住阵地，在只有最强者才能生存的世界中奋力坚持！</p>",
